    <item>
      <title>PC통신의 추억 - 곰주인 호스트 - 이야기5.3</title>
      <link>https://vasmani.github.io/post/2017-02-06-nostalgia-9600bps/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Feb 2017 11:01:38 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://vasmani.github.io/post/2017-02-06-nostalgia-9600bps/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;옛날 옛적 20년도 넘은 그 오래 전! 그때의 PC통신의 추억으로 빠져 보다!
효린이용 PC만들어 주기 프로젝트중, &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.dosbox.com/&#34;&gt;dosbox&lt;/a&gt;에 재미있는 기능들이 있어서 한 번 해 보았다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; padding-top: 30px; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;iframe src=&#34;//www.youtube.com/embed/fL7yuVpPjXA&#34; style=&#34;position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;&#34; allowfullscreen frameborder=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h2 id=&#34;server&#34;&gt;Server&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Raspberry Pi Model B&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Raspian&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dosbox&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;[sdl]
fullscreen=true
fulldouble=false
fullresolution=original
windowresolution=original
output=surface
autolock=true
sensitivity=100
waitonerror=true
priority=highest,normal
mapperfile=mapper-0.74.map
usescancodes=false

[dosbox]
language=
machine=svga_s3
captures=capture
memsize=16

[render]
frameskip=2
aspect=false
scaler=none

[cpu]
core=auto
cputype=386
cycles=3000
cycleup=10
cycledown=10

[mixer]
nosound=false
rate=8000
blocksize=2048
prebuffer=240

[midi]
mpu401=none
mididevice=default
midiconfig=

[sblaster]
sbtype=sb1
sbbase=220
irq=7
dma=1
hdma=5
sbmixer=true
oplmode=auto
oplemu=default
oplrate=22050

[gus]
gus=false
gusrate=44100
gusbase=240
gusirq=5
gusdma=3
ultradir=C:\ULTRASND

[speaker]
pcspeaker=true
pcrate=22050
tandy=auto
tandyrate=44100
disney=true

[joystick]
joysticktype=none
timed=true
autofire=false
swap34=false
buttonwrap=false

[modem]
modem=true
comport=1
listenport=23

[serial]
serial1=modem listenport:5000
serial2=dummy
serial3=disabled
serial4=disabled

[dos]
xms=true
ems=true
umb=true
keyboardlayout=auto

[ipx]
ipx=false

[autoexec]
@echo off
set path=c:\mdir
mount c /home/pi/dos
c:
m.exe
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;client&#34;&gt;Client&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OSX&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dosbox&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;[serial]
serial1=modem
serial2=dummy
serial3=disabled
serial4=disabled
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description>
